title: 'Insecure' Season 4 Exit Survey
description:
It was all going so well until Condola came along. We break down some things we did and didn't like from Season 4 of 'Insecure' and talk about what we want from Season 5.

Hosts: Chris Ryan, Haley O'Shaughnessy, and Jordan Ligons
